charisma.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394461106472,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394461139240,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394461172008,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/BetheGreatestRobertDowneyJr3PieceSet_2.webp?v=1765197641"},{"product_id":"why-so-serious-joker-3-piece-set","title":"Why so serious | Joker | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"299\" data-end=\"624\"\u003eCommand attention with this intense “Why So Serious?” cinematic villain poster set, inspired by one of the most unforgettable scenes in modern film history. Surrounded by neon-purple chaos and graffiti laughter, the artwork captures a chilling figure standing in the shadows — fearless, unpredictable, and dangerously iconic.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"626\" data-end=\"962\"\u003eThe bold typography, dark atmospheric backdrop, and menacing expression create a dramatic contrast that amplifies the poster’s psychological impact. With the haunting phrase \u003cstrong data-start=\"800\" data-end=\"821\"\u003e“WHY SO SERIOUS?”\u003c\/strong\u003e sprayed across the scene, this piece symbolizes rebellion, madness, and the magnetic charm of a character who rewrote the rules of villainy.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"964\" data-end=\"1110\"\u003eDesigned as a \u003cstrong data-start=\"978\" data-end=\"1002\"\u003e3-piece split poster\u003c\/strong\u003e, each panel strengthens the depth, mystery, and cinematic feel — making it a true centerpiece for any room.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1112\" data-end=\"1313\"\u003ePerfect for gaming setups, studios, bedrooms, or anyone who wants their space to reflect attitude, intensity, and the unforgettable legacy of a character known for chaos, brilliance, and dark charisma.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394460942632,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394460975400,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394461008168,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/WhysoseriousJoker3PieceSet_1.webp?v=1765275073"},{"product_id":"destiny-a-glorious-purpose-loki-3-piece-set","title":"Destiny | A Glorious Purpose | Loki | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp data-start=\"599\" data-end=\"922\"\u003eCommand attention with this striking \u003cstrong data-start=\"636\" data-end=\"724\"\u003e3-piece split wall poster inspired by the journey of destiny, sacrifice, and purpose\u003c\/strong\u003e. Designed in a cinematic arcane art style, the artwork captures a powerful moment of choice — a lone figure gripping glowing green energy, symbolizing timelines, responsibility, and transformation.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"924\" data-end=\"1244\"\u003eThe bold typography of \u003cstrong data-start=\"947\" data-end=\"960\"\u003e“DESTINY”\u003c\/strong\u003e anchors the composition, while the subtle line\u003cbr data-start=\"1007\" data-end=\"1010\"\u003e\u003cem data-start=\"1010\" data-end=\"1049\"\u003e“It is a glorious purpose you choose”\u003c\/em\u003e\u003cbr data-start=\"1049\" data-end=\"1052\"\u003eadds emotional depth and narrative weight. The blurred figure and focused hand create a dramatic sense of motion, sacrifice, and resolve — making this artwork more than décor, but a statement.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1246\" data-end=\"1544\"\u003ePrinted as a \u003cstrong data-start=\"1259\" data-end=\"1287\"\u003ethree-panel split poster\u003c\/strong\u003e, this piece adds depth and scale to your wall, making it ideal for bedrooms, studios, gaming setups, offices, or creative workspaces. The arcane green glow, minimal colour palette, and cinematic lighting ensure it stands out without overwhelming the space.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1546\" data-end=\"1777\"\u003eCrafted on \u003cstrong data-start=\"1557\" data-end=\"1596\"\u003e300 GSM premium matte texture paper\u003c\/strong\u003e, the poster delivers rich detail, smooth gradients, and long-lasting clarity with zero glare. Easy to install and designed to transform plain walls into powerful visual narratives.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp data-start=\"1779\" data-end=\"1896\"\u003ePerfect for fans of cinematic storytelling, character arcs, and motivational symbolism rooted in destiny and purpose.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51394460418344,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51394460451112,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51394460483880,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/DestinyAGloriousPurposeLoki3PieceSet_1.webp?v=1766040281"},{"product_id":"black-panther-legacy-blackpanther-3-piece-set","title":"Black Panther Legacy | Blackpanther | 3 Piece Set","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWakanda-inspired cinematic artwork featuring Black Panther in a powerful crossed-arm stance, surrounded by deep purple smoke and dark shadows.\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eHigh-contrast, bold composition designed to create a strong and premium wall presence with a clean split-panel aesthetic.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eProduct Details:\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003ePrinted on 300 GSM premium matte sheet\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e3-panel split design for a wide cinematic look\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDeep purple \u0026amp; black contrast with high detail finish\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eLightweight and easy to install\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFrame not included\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePerfect For:\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eGaming setups \u0026amp; desk backgrounds\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMarvel \/ superhero themed rooms\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDark aesthetic wall decor\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMinimal + bold statement setups\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cbr\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNote:\u003c\/strong\u003e Slight color variation may occur due to lighting and screen differences. Final print will match the design preview.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"Posterized","offers":[{"title":"A4","offer_id":51746510766376,"sku":null,"price":349.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"A3","offer_id":51746510799144,"sku":null,"price":399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"13X19\"","offer_id":51746510831912,"sku":null,"price":449.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0758\/7246\/9288\/files\/blackpanther1_22c3b291-1166-4186-8189-936711466fec.jpg?v=1777101350"}],"url":"https:\/\/www.posterized.in\/collections\/marvel-split-collections.oembed","provider":"Posterized","version":"1.0","type":"link"}